  "prompt": "What do you do on rainy days?",
  "response": "On rainy days, people often choose to stay indoors and enjoy cozy activities. Some popular activities include reading a book, watching movies or TV shows, cooking a comforting meal, or enjoying a warm beverage like tea or coffee. Others might use the opportunity to catch up on indoor hobbies such as knitting, painting, or playing an instrument, while some people might simply relish the sound of the rain and take the day to relax. If someone prefers being active, they might take the chance to visit a museum, go to the gym, or engage in indoor exercises like yoga. What do you like to do when it rains?",
